      "author": "ginkgobackup",
      "description": "## Removed\n- **定时全量备份**：从设置页移除「定时全量备份」开关与「全量备份间隔」滑块。Ginkgo Backup 桌面端已提供定时全量备份能力，插件层重复实现不再保留。底层 autoBackup / autoBackupIntervalMinutes 字段及 StagingManager.scheduleAutoBackup() / autoBackupTimer 一并删除。\n\n## Changed\n- **防抖延迟单位改为秒**：原 autoBackupDebounceMs（默认 30000ms）改为 autoBackupDebounceSec（默认 30s）。设置页滑块范围 5-120 秒。loadSettings 自动迁移旧配置（毫秒 → 秒）。\n\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/ginkgobackup/obsidian-ginkgo-backup/compare/0.5.9...0.5.10",
